## Verification Plan

### Manual Test
1. Chạy Narrative mode trên script Lepanto với niche "battle history"
2. Kiểm tra [_blueprint.json](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/7.Youtube/3.%20Battle%20History/1.%20Video%20doi%20thu/63%20How%20Christians%20Crushed%20the%20Ottoman%20Empire%20Battle%20of%20Lepanto%201571%20-%20Google%20T%C3%A0i%20li%E1%BB%87u/1/_blueprint.json) output có đủ:
   - Trận cánh Bắc (Barbarigo vs Siroco)
   - Geography structured
   - Tactical timeline
   - Weapon comparison cả 2 bên
